Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我们可能要离开一段时间\N{\rENG}All right, we may be a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.66,0:00:32.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可是...紫晶!\N{\rENG}But --Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.24,0:00:34.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥事?我忙着呢ˊ_>ˋ\N{\rENG}What? I'm busy.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶,保持警惕\N{\rENG}Amethyst,hold down the fort.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}知道啦～长官\N{\rENG}Aye, aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我负责期间绝不会有任何意外\N{\rENG}No surprises while I'm on duty.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.87,0:00:41.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥!\N{\rENG}Wha--!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.95,0:00:43.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}萨普莱斯!我早到啦～\N{\rENG}Surprise! I'm early!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.72,0:00:47.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我刚想告诉你 康妮约好了在今天进行剑术训练的\N{\rENG}I was trying to tell you Connie has sword training today.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}OMG 我全忘了!\N{\rENG}Oh! I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}非常抱歉 康妮\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.26,0:00:54.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噗嗤 ,"珍"不靠谱\N{\rENG} Very irresponsible, Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.30,0:00:55.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哼\N{\rENG} Mnh.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们是要去找铁石英吗?\N{\rENG}Is this because of Jasper?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}要调头去北方吗?\N{\rENG}Are you headed back north?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.27,0:00:59.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她依然在四处活动\N{\rENG}She's on the move.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们不能任由\N{\rENG}We can't have her just out there,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她到处刷怪!\N{\rENG}attacking random monsters for whatever reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.51,0:01:06.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然了!注意安全喔\N{\rENG}Of course. Be safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.98,0:01:08.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那可是我的专属台词\N{\rENG}That's my line.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶?-知道啦\N{\rENG}Amethyst? Got it.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们下周再进行训练吧\N{\rENG}We'll train next week
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只要铁石英不再让我们头疼\N{\rENG}without Jasper hanging over our heads.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.95,0:01:15.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是最理想的了\N{\rENG}Best-case scenario.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.99,0:01:20.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们这些幸运的家伙,逃过了训练日!\N{\rENG}Lucky break for you guys --You get the training day off.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.57,0:01:22.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以 接下来你们想干啥?\N{\rENG}So, what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢?哈?\N{\rENG}Oh? Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.47,0:01:35.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你开挂!\N{\rENG}Hey, no fair.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿嘿 紫晶 你看见那招了吗?\N{\rENG} Hey, Amethyst, did you see that?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶?\N{\rENG}Amethyst?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.43,0:01:43.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}咋了?\N{\rENG}'Sup?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.26,0:01:45.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你有在看我们训练吗?\N{\rENG}Are you even watching?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然咯 不然你觉得我在干嘛\N{\rENG}Sure. What's it look like?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得你没在看\N{\rENG}Like you're not watching.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.05,0:01:52.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}唔 尊讨厌\N{\rENG}Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.12,0:01:53.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}被你逮到了\N{\rENG}You got me.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.91,0:01:56.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在好多了吧～\N{\rENG}Is that better?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.23,0:01:59.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噫!-好恶\N{\rENG}Ew! Gross. Ew! Gross.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.06,0:02:00.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是-唔 确实好多了\N{\rENG}But, yeah, that's better.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来吧康妮  我们从头再来一遍\N{\rENG}Come on, Connie. Let's take it from the top.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.93,0:02:03.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的!\N{\rENG} Okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看到了吗?\N{\rENG} Did you see  that?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 那!\N{\rENG}Excellent! Amazing!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.92,0:02:22.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍是极好的\N{\rENG}Pearl-fect.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.75,0:02:27.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没有啦/w\ \N{\rENG}Ohh. I don't know. Not really.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.42,0:02:31.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的站姿完全是错的-力度也不够!\N{\rENG}My stance is all wrong, and my grip is a little soft.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么要纠结于这些小事?\N{\rENG}What are you worried about that little stuff for?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.70,0:02:37.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在战场上 这些根本无关紧要\N{\rENG}It's not gonna matter in a real fight.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这确实很重要\N{\rENG}It does, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.67,0:02:41.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我毁掉了我第一次魔法任务\N{\rENG}I blew it on my first real magical mission.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.87,0:02:45.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我直面那只宝石怪兽 却手足无措\N{\rENG}I was face-to-face with a monster, and I froze.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.94,0:02:51.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我之前用心一点训练的话 那次任务就不会失败了\N{\rENG}Maybe if I'd trained a little harder, I could have handled it.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在我看来 你就是想的太多了\N{\rENG}Sounds to me like you're too in your own head.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.72,0:02:57.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真正战斗的时候-每一秒都是难以预测的\N{\rENG}In a fight, you never know what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你只有临场发挥\N{\rENG}You just got to go with it.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不然你怎么能为那些\N{\rENG}How can you get ready when you don't even know
Dialogue: 600,0:03:01.47,0:03:03.76,Hint,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道的事做准备？what you're getting ready for, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 根本没有时间准备\N{\rENG}Yeah, you can't be ready.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.06,0:03:08.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你唯一需要做的事情 就是 放～轻～松～\N{\rENG}What you got to be is loose.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也想放轻松!\N{\rENG}I want to be loose!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后你就可以跟着感觉走了!\N{\rENG}Then you got to go with the flow.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.97,0:03:16.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}战斗靠的就是肚子深处的那种感觉!!\N{\rENG}Fighting's all about that feeling deep in your guts.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的肚肚感觉怎么样?\N{\rENG}What do your guts feel like?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}饿!\N{\rENG}Hungry.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也一样\N{\rENG}Mine, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来点零食!来点零食!\N{\rENG} Snack break. Snack break.
